descriptionHtml:
[font=Comic Sans MS][color=#c27ba0]     Hello guys :)[/color][color=#c27ba0]
     This MOD is just replacer for Ahlam and Nazeem from Whiterun.
[/color][color=#c27ba0]     Ahlam's meshes and Textures are standalone. CBBE and UNP body only.
     Nazeem's Head mesh, Head parts and Face textures are Standalone.
     (It mean without body. So you can use any male body types for your game.)
[/color][/font]
[color=#9900ff]     [/color][color=#ff0000][size=5]Important Notes[/size][/color]
[color=#ff0000][size=4]     This MOD is not support Wet and Cold MOD or something like that.
     If you use that, They will get Hair clipping with Hood from that MOD. Idk
     But Plz dont ask me support for that. I dont .... Sorry.
[/size][/color]

[color=#9900ff]
[size=2]     [/size][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]You can choose one file only from them :)[/size][/font][/color]
[font=Comic Sans MS][color=#c27ba0]     *Ahlam only file
     *Ahlam with Nazeem file
     *Nazeem only file[/color][/font]

     [font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ff0000]25/ 03/ 2016[/color][/font]
     [font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ff0000][size=4]Added Saffir and Amren to Optional file below.[/size][/color][/font]
[font=Comic Sans MS][color=#c27ba0]     Saffir's meshes and Textures are standalone. CBBE and UNP body only.
     Amren's Head mesh, Head parts and Face textures are Standalone.
     (Not include Ahlam and Nazeem.)

     [/color][color=#ff0000]28/ 03/ 2016[/color]
[color=#c27ba0]     [/color][color=#ff0000][size=4]Added Saadia to Optional file below.[/size][/color]
[color=#c27ba0]     [/color][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][color=#c27ba0]Saadia's meshes and Textures are standalone. CBBE and UNP body only.[/color][/font]
[font=Comic Sans MS][color=#c27ba0]     (little neck seem in under the some lighting. Sorry I can't fixed it anymore. but nvm plz :P)

[/color][/font]     [font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ff0000]30/ 03/ 2016 [/color][/font]
     [font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ff0000][size=5]Added new file "MyPeepsOfWhiterun" to Main files below. [/size][/color][/font]
[font=Comic Sans MS][color=#9900ff][size=2]     Include Ahlam, Saffir, Nazeem and Amren files. without Saadia.
     Actually this is not merged esp. 
     I made New esp and files. 
     If you install this, Plz remove previous files (MyAhlamWithNazeem and MySaffirWithAmren and etc...) 
[/size][/color][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=2][color=#9900ff]     before install MyPeepsOfWhiterun. [/color][/size]
[/font]
     [font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ff0000][size=2]01/04/2016[/size][/color][/font]
     [font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ff0000][size=5]Added New file "MyBro!!(Beta)" to Optional files below.[/size][/color][/font]
[font=Comic Sans MS][color=#9900ff]     Include Amren and Nazeem only.
     If you install this, Plz remove previous files (MyAhlamWithNazeem, MySaffirWithAmren)
     before install MyBro!!(Beta).
     If i made other NPCs, I will publish this as New MOD file. So (Beta) still now.[/color]
[/font]
    [font=Comic Sans MS] [color=#ff0000][size=2]20/04/2016 [/size][/color][/font]
     [font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ff0000][size=5]Added New files "MyAhlamWithFriends" to Optional files below.[/size]
[size=2]     [/size][size=5]This is Female NPCs only file.[/size][/color][/font]     [font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ff0000][size=5]Ahlam, Saffir, Saadia and Danica(New!!) only :)[/size][/color][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][color=#9900ff]  [/color][/font] 
     [font=Comic Sans MS][color=#9900ff]Plz unistall all previous version and files before install this.[/color][/font]
     [font=Comic Sans MS][color=#9900ff]If u wanna use also my Male NPCs replacer, U should use MyBro file from Optional files below.[/color][/font]

[font=Comic Sans MS]     [color=#ff0000][size=3]21/04/2016[/size][/color]
     [color=#ff0000][size=5]Fixed "MyAhlamWithFriends" files from Optional files below.[/size][/color]
     [color=#ff0000][size=5]Sorry, I made mistake about Saffir's Face tint Data. my bad....... [/size]
[size=2]     [/size][size=5]So now I fixed it.[/size][/color]
     [color=#ff0000][size=5]Plz unistall v1.0, and then Install v1.0F. thanks.[/size][/color][/font]
